Q5. Sum of N natural numbers

The sum of n natural numbers is :

Choose the correct answer from below:
A) (n*(n+1))/2
B) (n*(n-1))/2
C) (n+1)/2
D) (n*(n+1)*(2*n+1))/6

Ans:A) (n*(n+1))/2
Complete solution : As the first n natural numbers are 1,2,3,4,5,6,.........n
They form an AP with a=1 and d=1
The sum of AP for n numbers = ((2*a + (n-1)*d)*n)/2
=((2 + n - 1)*n)/2
=(n*(n+1))/2